messages.content: Unlike the Conservative Government of the 1980s we won't walk on by in difficult times. I'm determined to ensure we deliver fairness for all in recovery.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: A brand new world class hospital, Coventry's new University Hospital has brought local people the quality health care they deserve.
Nineteen Children's Centres have opened across Coventry with four more on the way, ten schools are also being rebuilt or refurbished across the city.
Free swimming available to all under 16s and over 60s across Coventry.
